text: Wingersheim-les-Quatre-Bans is a commune. It is in Grand Est in the Bas-Rhin department in northeast France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2016 and consists of the former communes of Wingersheim (the seat), Gingsheim, Hohatzenheim and Mittelhausen.Arrêté 21 December 2015 == References == Category:2016 establishments in France Category:Communes in Bas-Rhin
